00:51:00,511 --> 00:51:02,582
By any chance,

695
00:51:02,582 --> 00:51:06,051
do you know what his flight number is?

696
00:51:14,792 --> 00:51:16,931
Okay. Thank you, Grandma.

697
00:51:16,931 --> 00:51:19,661
I'll call you again next time.

698
00:51:19,661 --> 00:51:21,372
Bye.

