00:53:27,261 --> 00:53:29,292
 Of course. 

731
00:53:29,292 --> 00:53:32,062
 No one will be able to believe me. 

732
00:53:32,702 --> 00:53:35,271
 Not that I am from the future. 

733
00:53:35,271 --> 00:53:38,232
 That I already know everything that will happen 

734
00:53:38,971 --> 00:53:41,372
 from now on. 

735
00:53:42,941 --> 00:53:45,882
   

736
00:53:45,882 --> 00:53:50,651
 It's even hard for me to believe everything that's happening now. 

737
00:53:55,952 --> 00:53:58,961
Grandma, open the door, please.

738
00:53:58,961 --> 00:54:01,361
We have no time, Grandma!

