749
00:54:37,431 --> 00:54:41,031
A way for a shrimp to beat the whales.

750
00:54:41,031 --> 00:54:45,572
Once you see this note, I believe that you will

751
00:54:45,572 --> 00:54:47,841
change your flight.

752
00:54:54,511 --> 00:54:57,781
- Great work. 
 - Great work.

